    "contract": {
        "name": "CollateralXStablecoinController",
        "desc": "Stablecoin control skeleton.\n\nSafety-critical assumption: this app stores stablecoin control metadata only.\nASA creation, clawback/freeze roles, and mint/burn inner transactions are left\nfor a later phase so asset authority can be designed and tested separately.",
        "methods": [
